{"tid":2440846,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黎智英李柱銘等人涉8.18未經批准遊行 胡雅文裁定案件表證成立 辯方明天交代會否傳召證人","createTime":"2021-03-10T08:48:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T09:57:53.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"363033b10fb160ae5cbaabb4ba48fe3fb9e0b37e","tid":2440846,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T08:48:36.000Z","msg":"李柱銘及黎智英等九名泛民主派人士被控前年8月18日維園反警暴集會當天，在港島組織及參與未經批准遊行，案件今在西九龍裁判法院續審。辯方盤問警民關係組總督察，問及當日警方是否應指引集會人士如何離場，總督察答：「有出口走就走㗎啦，唔需要有人去教。」而負責主持聯絡會議的總督察承認，民陣在會上提議以遊行達到流水式疏散效果，但他沒有就此向上級匯報。<br />\n<br />\n法官胡雅文裁定案件表面證供成立，辯方將於明天交代會否傳召證人。<br />\n<br />\n早前作供的東區警民關係組總督察胡敏儀，今繼續接受盤問。辯方問及8.18維園集會的疏散方法，並問警方是否應該指引集會人士離開。胡答：「有出口走就走㗎啦，唔需要有人去教。」至於集會人士眾多，疏散會否緩慢或有危險，胡亦不同意，表示當日沒收到危險報告，並說：「如果我係參加者，我會去北面離開，嗰度應該少啲人。」<br />\n<br />\n警方預計集會人士經銅鑼灣和天后港鐵站離開，辯方問兩個站能否消化所有群眾，胡說以她所知，車站當天有運作，消化視乎時間，「冇話唔得㗎，運作緊㗎嘛」。辯方問人多會否產生公眾危險，胡稱：「我冇諗過，港鐵站好多時都好多人。」胡不同意辯方所指，自己的聯絡工作包括就人群管理與運輸署及港鐵溝通，亦不同意警方沒有協助市民進出維園，令民陣要自行盡力疏散群眾。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210310/KMLJUIVQGFCTLNKF3HZXFIR374/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210310%2FKMLJUIVQGFCTLNKF3HZXFIR374%2F&d=QSug7dhZHD7voFbR5lwplVSbRuvIKfaxuJHhOs3YWJk%3D&h=b7a319af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210310%2FKMLJUIVQGFCTLNKF3HZXFIR374%2F&h=21b2c1bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210310/KMLJUIVQGFCTLNKF3HZXFIR374/</a>"},{"pid":"6f1441299ad1ec9514657fe6c3e0f99643d4a453","tid":2440846,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T08:52:55.000Z","msg":"木頭JJ 紅過練狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fc0eb3358b3f618c21215231710c8a19beded24","tid":2440846,"uid":110043,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T08:53:16.000Z","msg":"胡狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc14fc1210b455ad0c538e6cd452ea1517faae4e","tid":2440846,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T09:04:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f5f3f515dcec47abc4615b10400b4fe4233f101","tid":2440846,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T09:50:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3267b7c441eebd50d5f3ebbd9f515fc729cd01b5","tid":2440846,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T09:57:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}